Sept 3 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Wednesday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

BARCLAYS SECURITIES JAPAN LTD  The unit of Barclays Plc <BARC.L> said it appointed Kazunori Ito technology analyst in its Japan equity research team. [ID:nL3N0R43FK]  AVIVA INVESTORS  The global asset management business of Aviva Plc <AV.L> appointed David Lis as chief investment officer for equities and multi-assets. [ID:nL3N0R432P]  CARMIGNAC GROUP The European asset management firm said it hired Fabian Herzog as a business development manager in its Switzerland team. [ID:nL3N0R4383]  SAXO CAPITAL MARKETS UK LTD